{"tid":675382,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿ 雲加：曾拒皇馬兩三次 不想在困難期背叛阿仙奴","createTime":"2018-05-23T12:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T11:37:27.000Z","uid":11081,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f1cee62bb5cf72b560108e6675862efbb9d18086","tid":675382,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"雲加近日接受採訪時表示自己曾經拒絕了皇馬連三次的邀約，原因就是自己要忠於阿仙奴，在兵工廠仍在未新球場償還債務的敏感時期，自己不想背叛阿仙奴。<br />\n<br />\n　　雲加說：「當我們建造新球場時，銀行要求我承諾留隊五年。我第一次拒絕皇馬的時間，還在這五年之內，我覺得我不能那麼做，那是背叛阿仙奴。」　<br />\n<br />\n　　雲加繼續說道「你們知道，我總共拒絕了皇馬兩三次，皇馬是我小時候最喜歡的球隊之一，只是我覺得當時那個時候對阿仙奴是非常敏感的一個時期。你總是想要執教皇馬這樣的球隊，因為當時他們給了我掌控整個球會的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反雲必需死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2aceee716df4c097bb7f19798251e7796e7f7c","tid":675382,"uid":11081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:50:47.000Z","msg":"沒有雲加的阿仙奴...不再是阿仙奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2939c39eb6457525d57670a2cf92d0d7852941ee","tid":675382,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"Yaya<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8064e538a6dfaeeec2494779823c0fdf0b6ff9","tid":675382,"uid":33660,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"有錢洗嘅雲加&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;哥狗+摩狗+高普"},{"pid":"d2bc82baca6559ebda56cdf5c6c731ad6e2a89cc","tid":675382,"uid":18646,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0b8064e538a6dfaeeec2494779823c0fdf0b6ff9","tid":675382,"uid":33660,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"有錢洗嘅雲加&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;哥狗+摩狗+高普"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"39f7240bce3915f5ad1cbceb322673c2ff